title: Aries By Zenith E-Juice
description: Aries is the perfect juice for anyone who loves vanilla and custard. Your tongue will be sent to heaven as warm vanilla and sugary sweetness delight your mouth. The first inhale will make your mouth water and leave you craving another. Then your cravings will be satisfied as Aries drenches your taste buds in rich, creamy, sweet vanilla custard sauce. The exhale tops it off by flooding your palate with sweet goodness, providing an extra power pack of butteriness to boot. With a perfectly fulfilling finish, Aries is the flavor for vanilla custard and cream vape enthusiasts.
